{
  "texts": [
    "In this handbook, two recipe book editors give punctual recommendations on how to write a good recipe in terms of the learning objectives (structure, specificity, and clarity).",
    "We use the keywords \"specify\" and \"indicate\" to retrieve 45 suggestions from the handbook.",
    "Table 2 lists all the domain-general suggestions as well as examples of domain-specific suggestions.",
    "There are four suggestions related to the structure and three suggestions related to the clarity of the text.",
    "For these two categories, there is a direct mapping between domain-general and domain-specific annotations."
  ]
}